{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/yi-yuan-wei-shi-yao-xu-yao-wu-ding-lu-hua-zhe-ji-dian-hao-chu-ni-bu-de-bu-zhi/","webpackCompilationHash":"6aeeaaa382e6a1351e99","result":{"data":{"ghostPost":{"id":"Ghost__Post__5d11c01395f47f36568540c2","title":"医院为什么需要屋顶绿化？这几点好处，你不得不知！","slug":"yi-yuan-wei-shi-yao-xu-yao-wu-ding-lu-hua-zhe-ji-dian-hao-chu-ni-bu-de-bu-zhi","featured":false,"feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/2_meitu_2-6.jpg","excerpt":"城市越来越大，好的医院却越来越少。且很多医院都是钢筋水泥不见一点自然，整体给感觉也是冷冰冰没有温度。","custom_excerpt":"城市越来越大，好的医院却越来越少。且很多医院都是钢筋水泥不见一点自然，整体给感觉也是冷冰冰没有温度。","created_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","published_at_pretty":"25 June, 2019","updated_at_pretty":"27 June, 2019","created_at":"2019-06-25T14:32:51.000+08:00","published_at":"2019-06-25T14:34:56.000+08:00","updated_at":"2019-06-27T12:48:15.000+08:00","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"og_description":null,"og_image":null,"og_title":null,"twitter_description":null,"twitter_image":null,"twitter_title":null,"authors":[{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"}],"primary_author":{"name":"Jason","slug":"jason","bio":null,"profile_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/icons8-customer-100.png","twitter":null,"facebook":null,"website":"https://new.a-green.cn"},"primary_tag":{"name":"屋面绿化","slug":"wu-mian-lu-hua","description":"屋顶绿化、屋面绿化、屋顶花园、屋顶草坪、屋面草坪","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/3.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"},"tags":[{"name":"屋面绿化","slug":"wu-mian-lu-hua","description":"屋顶绿化、屋面绿化、屋顶花园、屋顶草坪、屋面草坪","feature_image":"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/08/3.jpeg","meta_description":null,"meta_title":null,"visibility":"public"}],"plaintext":"城市越来越大，好的医院却越来越少。且很多医院都是钢筋水泥不见一点自然，整体给感觉也是冷冰冰没有温度。对于术后身体处于恢复阶段的患者来说，这无疑增加了患者的恢复周期变长。\n\n在泰国很多医院会对楼顶进行开发，将其打造成一个郁郁葱葱的小花园。而这个小花园的作用是为医院患者提供修养身心的地方。这样的设计增加的了医院的自然生机，同时也为医院提供了非常棒的休息区。\n\n\n目前，国内景观少的原因主要是地价贵和维护麻烦。将医院开发成屋顶花园，会增加医院的运营成本，所以很少有医院去推行这种绿化方式。\n\n这种将平面绿化转化成屋顶的方式，虽然给医院增加了运营的负担。但绿色景观更助于病人的身心恢复，同时也提升了医院的环境与形象。\n\n绿色环境对病人病情恢复有明显帮助，这减少了其对医疗资源的占用，让更多的患者可以得到有效的治疗。\n\n在很多发达国家，许多医院开始将这这种方案应用到实际中。如泰国·Ramathibodi愈合花园、美国·Oakville-Trafalgar纪念医院、新加坡·绿洲梯田项目等......","html":"<p>城市越来越大，好的医院却越来越少。且很多医院都是钢筋水泥不见一点自然，整体给感觉也是冷冰冰没有温度。对于术后身体处于恢复阶段的患者来说，这无疑增加了患者的恢复周期变长。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/1_meitu_1-6.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>在泰国很多医院会对楼顶进行开发，将其打造成一个郁郁葱葱的小花园。而这个小花园的作用是为医院患者提供修养身心的地方。这样的设计增加的了医院的自然生机，同时也为医院提供了非常棒的休息区。<br></p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/2_meitu_2-5.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>目前，国内景观少的原因主要是地价贵和维护麻烦。将医院开发成屋顶花园，会增加医院的运营成本，所以很少有医院去推行这种绿化方式。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/3_meitu_3-5.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>这种将平面绿化转化成屋顶的方式，虽然给医院增加了运营的负担。但绿色景观更助于病人的身心恢复，同时也提升了医院的环境与形象。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/4_meitu_4-7.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>绿色环境对病人病情恢复有明显帮助，这减少了其对医疗资源的占用，让更多的患者可以得到有效的治疗。</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/5_meitu_5-7.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image--><p>在很多发达国家，许多医院开始将这这种方案应用到实际中。如泰国·Ramathibodi愈合花园、美国·Oakville-Trafalgar纪念医院、新加坡·绿洲梯田项目等......</p><!--kg-card-begin: image--><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://new.a-green.cn/content/images/2019/06/6_meitu_6-6.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\"></figure><!--kg-card-end: image-->","url":"https://new.a-green.cn/yi-yuan-wei-shi-yao-xu-yao-wu-ding-lu-hua-zhe-ji-dian-hao-chu-ni-bu-de-bu-zhi/","uuid":"e493f0c0-b034-4f67-b9ef-f35050f50bfb","page":false,"codeinjection_foot":null,"codeinjection_head":null,"codeinjection_styles":null,"comment_id":"5d11c01395f47f36568540c2"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"yi-yuan-wei-shi-yao-xu-yao-wu-ding-lu-hua-zhe-ji-dian-hao-chu-ni-bu-de-bu-zhi"}}}